# alex-cv ‚Äî architecture & tooling

## Layout

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ assets/main.css       # @import "tailwindcss" + @theme
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/layout/    # AppHeader, AppFooter
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/sections/  # one file = one landing section
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/ui/        # AppButton, AppContainer, NavLink, CaseCard
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ layouts/DefaultLayout.vue
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ pages/                # file-based routes
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ router/index.ts
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ App.vue               # <RouterView /> only
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ main.ts
```

**Page rule:** A page is only `<DefaultLayout>` + section (or case) imports. No layout spacing/classes on the page file ‚Äî sections own container and spacing.

## Routing

- `vite.config.ts`: `VueRouter({ routesFolder: 'src/pages' })` **before** `vue()`.
- `router/index.ts`: `import { routes } from 'vue-router/auto-routes'`.
- `typed-router.d.ts` at repo root, in `tsconfig.app.json` `include`; `moduleResolution: "bundler"`.

## Tailwind v4

- Config only in `src/assets/main.css` (no `tailwind.config.js` / `postcss.config.js`).
- Use built-in `container` as-is; center with `container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6` (see `AppContainer.vue`).
- Fonts: `Work Sans`, `Inter` via `<link>` in `index.html`.

## Lint

oxlint (`.oxlintrc.json`) then eslint (`eslint.config.ts`). Pages/layouts: `vue/multi-word-component-names: off` for `index.vue` / `[...path].vue`. Prettier last via `eslint-config-prettier`; `.prettierrc`: singleQuote, no semi, `trailingComma: all`, `printWidth: 100`.
